a:["$","div",null,{"className":"flex gap-8 px-8 py-10 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto","children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"flex-1 min-w-0 prose prose-neutral max-w-none prose-headings:scroll-mt-20 prose-a:text-hr-primary prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline prose-code:before:content-none prose-code:after:content-none","children":"$L14"}],["$","aside",null,{"className":"hidden xl:block w-64 shrink-0","children":["$","$L15",null,{"source":"\n## Introduction\n\nCreate your account, post your first job, and invite team members.\n\n## Step 1: Create your account\n\nGo to hr.bg and click Start free trial. Enter your work email and password. Complete the onboarding form.\n\n## Step 2: Post your first job\n\nOpen Recruitment, Jobs, Create job. Fill in title, location, department, and description. Click Publish.\n\n## Step 3: Invite your team\n\nGo to Settings, Team, Invite user. Enter email and choose role: Admin, HR, Recruiter, or Hiring manager.\n\n## Next steps\n\n- [Core HR](/docs/features/core-hr) — Import employees or add them manually.\n- [Leave](/docs/features/leave) — Configure leave types.\n- [Payroll](/docs/features/payroll) — Set up Bulgarian tax and NRA compliance.\n"}]}]]}]
